Class GeodeticDatum

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.geo.GeodeticDatum
public class GeodeticDatum extends Object
A geodetic datum is an ellipsoid which is an approximation of the shape of the Earth.
Author:
Douglas Lau
